Sentencas: A potential high-performance solid oxide fuel cell cathode material, Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta, was synthesized by a solid-state reaction method.
Titulo: Influence of CO2 on Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ at elevated temperatures

Sentencas: As atmospheric CO2 may degrade its cathodic performance, the reaction of this material to different gas atmospheres was measured by thermogravimetric analysis.
Titulo: Influence of CO2 on Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ at elevated temperatures

Sentencas: Powder particles were characterized by transmission electron microscopy, energy-dispersive X-ray spectroscopy and electron energy-loss spectroscopy, and the formation of a carbonate layer was found.
Titulo: Influence of CO2 on Ba0.2Sr0.8Co0.8Fe0.2O3-δ at elevated temperatures
